Items.Content: I actually grew up drawing with the creator of these images. When I was 13 he hosted a website called The Island Closest to Heaven. It was a collective drawing board that you could all draw on at the same time across the internet. I fell in love with these types of boards and followed Eric for quite some time. His artwork is normally done in Photoshop with a Wacom tablet. Copyright for images are 2013-2016. His works can be found at http://tsaoshin.deviantart.com
